<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Wildwood</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
        <p class="par-lg">Established in 1956 on a plateau located to the south of the Bow River Valley, Wildwood is a breathtaking residential community in the South West quadrant of Calgary. </p>
        <p class="par-xl">Offering some of the most stunning views of the river valley, Wildwood is fast becoming one of the most popular choices for homebuyers and investors alike.</p>
        <p class="par-lg">Residents in Wildwood are provided with a myriad of recreational options from walking and hiking trails, outdoor rinks to baseball diamonds and tennis courts to enjoy their leisurely hours.</p>
        </div>
